* Add Blur/Sharpen image filters.                                  <planed by Gilles Caulier for 0.6.3>
* Added dockable toolbars.
* Add Plugins interface.
* Add Blur/Sharpen image filters.
* Add image Histogram viewer.
* Add Colors autocorrection filter.


